280
00:23:31,640 --> 00:23:33,550
All the goods of our Wangquan Manor

281
00:23:33,550 --> 00:23:34,960
bear protective talismans.

282
00:23:34,960 --> 00:23:36,220
Falling from the tree?

283
00:23:37,510 --> 00:23:38,970
You must be seeking death!

284
00:23:42,200 --> 00:23:43,070
Sorry, Lady Hero.

285
00:23:43,070 --> 00:23:44,000
I have to go!

286
00:23:44,860 --> 00:23:46,890
[Cloth]

287
00:23:45,550 --> 00:23:46,550
Stop right there!

288
00:23:52,880 --> 00:23:53,720
My dress!

289
00:23:54,110 --> 00:23:54,970
You want to die?

290
00:23:55,350 --> 00:23:57,210
Please, Lady Hero, don't kill me!

291
00:23:57,550 --> 00:23:58,200
Lady Hero.

292
00:23:58,640 --> 00:24:01,480
I noticed there're many patches
on your dress.

293
00:24:01,920 --> 00:24:04,480
It must be very important to you.

294
00:24:04,590 --> 00:24:05,850
As long as you spare me,

295
00:24:05,920 --> 00:24:07,200
I promise I'll mend it

296
00:24:07,200 --> 00:24:09,660
and make it even more beautiful
than before.

297
00:24:09,720 --> 00:24:10,590
Please.

298
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:11,880
Spare my life.

299
00:24:13,440 --> 00:24:14,770
What are you looking at?

300
00:24:15,640 --> 00:24:16,040
Sorry.

301
00:24:17,400 --> 00:24:17,960
Okay?

302
00:24:21,400 --> 00:24:22,400
You said

303
00:24:24,030 --> 00:24:25,070
you could mend it?

304
00:24:26,590 --> 00:24:27,000
Yes.

305
00:24:33,200 --> 00:24:34,070
Lady Hero.

306
00:24:34,440 --> 00:24:36,590
I've mended your dress.

307
00:24:36,920 --> 00:24:38,640
Please spare my life.

308
00:24:40,960 --> 00:24:42,720
Seeing how happy you are, Lady Hero,

309
00:24:42,720 --> 00:24:44,640
I can mend any other clothes or dresses

310
00:24:44,640 --> 00:24:45,680
that get torn as well.

311
00:24:45,680 --> 00:24:47,000
Please spare my life.

312
00:24:48,240 --> 00:24:50,720
What kind of person do you think I,
Feng Tingyun, am?

313
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:52,720
This dress is the only exception.

314
00:24:52,880 --> 00:24:54,350
It was a gift from my master.

315
00:24:54,350 --> 00:24:56,790
Seeing how simple your room is, Lady Hero,

316
00:24:56,790 --> 00:24:57,640
I guess

317
00:24:57,640 --> 00:24:59,240
you don't have many dresses.

318
00:24:59,440 --> 00:25:00,700
As long as you let me go,

319
00:25:00,720 --> 00:25:02,720
I'll weave a prettier dress for you.

320
00:25:02,880 --> 00:25:03,830
What do you think?

321
00:25:03,830 --> 00:25:05,270
You know how to weave as well?

322
00:25:05,270 --> 00:25:06,240
Of course.

323
00:25:06,590 --> 00:25:07,750
Weaving brocade from demon silk

324
00:25:07,750 --> 00:25:09,590
is a required skill for us little spiders.

325
00:25:09,590 --> 00:25:10,830
No matter how intricate

326
00:25:10,830 --> 00:25:12,000
or beautiful the pattern,

327
00:25:12,000 --> 00:25:13,030
I can weave it.

328
00:25:19,510 --> 00:25:20,510
Then can you weave

329
00:25:21,070 --> 00:25:22,070
this dress for me?

330
00:25:25,270 --> 00:25:26,720
This...

331
00:25:26,720 --> 00:25:28,680
Isn't this a costume?

332
00:25:29,200 --> 00:25:30,000
And

333
00:25:30,270 --> 00:25:32,600
it's the kind
that an old widow would wear.

334
00:25:34,960 --> 00:25:36,220
Can you weave it or not?

335
00:25:36,440 --> 00:25:37,110
Yes, I can.

336
00:25:37,350 --> 00:25:37,920
I can.

337
00:25:38,640 --> 00:25:39,880
Lady Hero,

338
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:42,000
are you planning to meet someone important

339
00:25:42,000 --> 00:25:43,720
in this dress?

340
00:25:44,160 --> 00:25:46,400
My senior's birthday is in a few days.

341
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:48,610
I want to wear this on his birthday.

342
00:25:49,680 --> 00:25:52,270
If you can weave it,

343
00:25:54,480 --> 00:25:55,510
I'll let you go.

344
00:25:56,310 --> 00:25:57,000
Great!

345
00:25:57,160 --> 00:25:58,360
Thank you, Lady Hero.

346
00:25:59,720 --> 00:26:00,320
Lady Hero,

347
00:26:00,640 --> 00:26:01,830
is that

348
00:26:02,030 --> 00:26:03,680
a letter for your senior?

349
00:26:04,200 --> 00:26:04,680
Yes.

350
00:26:05,240 --> 00:26:06,960
I write one for him every year,
but he never reads them.

351
00:26:06,960 --> 00:26:09,160
And he never allows anyone to
celebrate his birthday.

352
00:26:09,160 --> 00:26:10,000
But it's okay.

353
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:11,270
Loving him

354
00:26:11,270 --> 00:26:12,400
is my own business.

355
00:26:12,830 --> 00:26:14,310
I'll keep writing them anyway.

356
00:26:14,310 --> 00:26:15,350
I see.

357
00:26:16,160 --> 00:26:17,820
How about I deliver the letter

358
00:26:18,160 --> 00:26:19,270
for you this year?

359
00:26:22,240 --> 00:26:23,200
My senior

360
00:26:24,480 --> 00:26:25,590
is

361
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:27,680
a Soldier.

362
00:26:28,270 --> 00:26:29,070
A Soldier?

363
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:33,310
You said he's a Soldier?

364
00:26:33,680 --> 00:26:34,240
Then...

365
00:26:35,000 --> 00:26:35,800
Will a Soldier

366
00:26:36,400 --> 00:26:38,200
kill a poor little spider demon?

367
00:26:38,790 --> 00:26:39,880
A poor,

368
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:42,790
injured little spider demon.

369
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:14,350
How unlucky.

370
00:27:15,310 --> 00:27:17,370
The Soldier didn't notice me, did he?

371
00:27:20,830 --> 00:27:21,960
Safe. Good.

372
00:27:22,790 --> 00:27:24,070
Come on, No.12580.

373
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:26,410
Just drop the letter and leave,

374
00:27:26,480 --> 00:27:27,540
and you'll be safe.

375
00:27:28,790 --> 00:27:29,320
Alright.

376
00:27:29,590 --> 00:27:30,350
I can do it.

377
00:27:31,270 --> 00:27:33,680
I'm the best little spider of Silk Cave,

378
00:27:33,750 --> 00:27:34,830
No.12580.

379
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:37,070
Delivering letters is

380
00:27:36,620 --> 00:27:38,440
[To Senior]

381
00:27:37,400 --> 00:27:39,260
a task I can handle effortlessly.

382
00:27:58,590 --> 00:28:00,680
I'm so unlucky today.

383
00:28:01,440 --> 00:28:02,270
Soldier?

384
00:28:15,350 --> 00:28:15,960
Why

385
00:28:16,400 --> 00:28:17,310
is she here?

386
00:28:18,680 --> 00:28:20,410
There's a barrier in this yard.

387
00:28:20,640 --> 00:28:21,750
How did you get in?

388
00:28:22,310 --> 00:28:23,710
I didn't mean to barge in.

389
00:28:23,880 --> 00:28:24,790
It was Lady Feng.

390
00:28:24,790 --> 00:28:26,110
She gave me a pass

391
00:28:26,200 --> 00:28:28,200
and asked me to deliver you a letter.

392
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:31,480
Please, Soldier.

393
00:28:31,720 --> 00:28:32,680
Just accept it,

394
00:28:33,000 --> 00:28:35,060
or I'll have to suffer when I get back.

395
00:28:36,380 --> 00:28:44,410
[To Senior]

396
00:28:38,750 --> 00:28:39,550
Don't go.

397
00:28:39,920 --> 00:28:40,880
At least accept

398
00:28:41,070 --> 00:28:42,400
Lady Feng's letter.

399
00:28:42,720 --> 00:28:43,110
Hey!

400
00:28:45,310 --> 00:28:47,350
I'll definitely die if I go back
like this.

401
00:28:47,350 --> 00:28:48,270
No.12580.

402
00:28:48,310 --> 00:28:50,160
The time for life or death has come.

403
00:28:50,160 --> 00:28:51,020
I'll go all out.

404
00:28:52,280 --> 00:28:54,210
[To Senior]

405
00:29:01,020 --> 00:29:02,330
[To Senior]

406
00:29:04,620 --> 00:29:06,190
[To Senior]

407
00:29:11,300 --> 00:29:17,340
[To Senior]

408
00:29:21,350 --> 00:29:23,480
Get out of here if you don't want to die!

409
00:29:24,070 --> 00:29:26,270
Just give it a read! What's the big deal?

410
00:29:27,550 --> 00:29:28,080
I'm sorry

411
00:29:28,200 --> 00:29:29,720
for being a little loud,

412
00:29:30,400 --> 00:29:32,440
but I've opened the letter for you.

413
00:29:32,680 --> 00:29:34,310
Lady Feng asked to meet you

414
00:29:34,310 --> 00:29:35,750
by the garden pond
on the night of the 3rd.

415
00:29:35,750 --> 00:29:36,310
The 3rd.

416
00:29:36,480 --> 00:29:37,480
It's tomorrow, you know?

417
00:29:37,480 --> 00:29:38,200
I can read.

418
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:40,450
Promise me you'll be there.

419
00:29:41,070 --> 00:29:41,550
Get out.

420
00:29:42,160 --> 00:29:42,640
Got it.

421
00:29:46,430 --> 00:29:47,960
What a beautiful sunset.

422
00:30:00,920 --> 00:30:02,050
At this time of year,

423
00:30:02,640 --> 00:30:04,270
the rhododendrons on Mount Baiwu

424
00:30:04,270 --> 00:30:05,830
should be in full bloom.

425
00:30:07,240 --> 00:30:09,830
It's a truly gorgeous sight.

426
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:11,000
I wonder

427
00:30:11,790 --> 00:30:13,320
if I'll ever have the chance

428
00:30:13,480 --> 00:30:14,510
to go back there.

429
00:30:15,640 --> 00:30:16,240
All right.

430
00:30:16,510 --> 00:30:17,040
Soldier.

431
00:30:17,310 --> 00:30:18,040
I'm leaving.

432
00:30:18,070 --> 00:30:19,440
Remember to go.

433
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:20,720
For this date with you, Lady Feng

434
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:22,310
prepared a really beautiful dress.

435
00:30:22,310 --> 00:30:23,200
You must go.

436
00:30:23,350 --> 00:30:24,350
Promise me, okay?

437
00:30:24,480 --> 00:30:25,030
Bye.

438
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:30,440
A truly...

439
00:30:31,550 --> 00:30:33,240
A truly gorgeous sight, is it?

440
00:30:44,440 --> 00:30:45,310
Lady Feng.

441
00:30:45,750 --> 00:30:47,480
You've put a bit too much makeup

442
00:30:47,680 --> 00:30:49,270
on your face, don't you think?

443
00:30:49,270 --> 00:30:50,440
It's okay.

444
00:30:50,510 --> 00:30:51,640
As long as I like it.

445
00:30:52,270 --> 00:30:53,960
Although I like Senior very much,

446
00:30:53,960 --> 00:30:55,200
I won't change myself

447
00:30:55,270 --> 00:30:56,240
because of him.

448
00:30:57,440 --> 00:30:59,100
I'm the chief female disciple

449
00:30:59,110 --> 00:31:00,710
of Wangquan Manor after all.

450
00:31:05,200 --> 00:31:05,680
I'm off.

451
00:31:10,270 --> 00:31:12,110
Always being herself.

452
00:31:12,680 --> 00:31:13,480
That's great.

453
00:31:20,680 --> 00:31:23,000
Why is Lady Feng back so soon?

454
00:31:24,480 --> 00:31:25,680
You're back.

455
00:31:25,680 --> 00:31:26,400
Lady Feng.

456
00:31:27,070 --> 00:31:28,110
What happened?

457
00:31:28,830 --> 00:31:30,630
Didn't you go to see your senior?

458
00:31:31,550 --> 00:31:33,240
He didn't come.

459
00:31:34,200 --> 00:31:35,830
He sent someone else there

460
00:31:36,110 --> 00:31:37,000
and asked me

461
00:31:37,000 --> 00:31:38,720
to practice my sword properly.

462
00:31:38,720 --> 00:31:39,880
Your senior

463
00:31:40,270 --> 00:31:41,870
has really gone a bit too far.

464
00:31:42,750 --> 00:31:43,880
But it's okay.

465
00:31:44,750 --> 00:31:45,830
My senior

466
00:31:46,150 --> 00:31:49,960
must like someone who's particularly
good at swordsmanship.

467
00:31:50,590 --> 00:31:52,200
I, Feng Tingyun,

468
00:31:52,640 --> 00:31:54,790
will definitely become

469
00:31:55,640 --> 00:31:56,750
the strongest swordsman

470
00:31:56,750 --> 00:31:58,950
in the Yiqi Alliance—strongest of all!

471
00:31:59,550 --> 00:32:00,400
I can do it!

472
00:32:02,680 --> 00:32:03,640
I'm sure...

473
00:32:03,960 --> 00:32:04,620
I'm sure...

474
00:32:05,350 --> 00:32:06,590
I'm sure I can do it.

475
00:32:09,310 --> 00:32:10,640
Lady Feng,

476
00:32:11,110 --> 00:32:12,640
you're really incredible.

477
00:32:12,640 --> 00:32:14,310
You're not discouraged at all.

478
00:32:14,310 --> 00:32:15,640
Even after he treated you like that,

479
00:32:15,640 --> 00:32:17,100
you're still so positive.

480
00:32:20,240 --> 00:32:21,040
This won't do.

481
00:32:21,680 --> 00:32:23,680
I can't just stand by and do nothing.

482
00:32:30,350 --> 00:32:31,550
Logically speaking,

483
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,400
no one is allowed to touch

484
00:32:33,510 --> 00:32:34,960
Master's Jinlan Mask.

485
00:32:35,310 --> 00:32:36,480
But I

486
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:37,880
didn't see anything.

487
00:32:39,790 --> 00:32:40,550
Mr. Fei.

488
00:32:43,200 --> 00:32:45,800
This mask was a gift
from my mother to my father.

489
00:32:45,830 --> 00:32:47,630
Although my mother passed away,

490
00:32:49,510 --> 00:32:50,350
my father

491
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:53,880
has never forgotten her,
even for a moment.

492
00:32:55,550 --> 00:32:56,590
How can you tell?

493
00:32:57,240 --> 00:33:00,040
My father doesn't allow anyone
to touch this mask,

494
00:33:01,240 --> 00:33:03,300
yet it remains spotless at all times.

495
00:33:04,160 --> 00:33:05,160
So, Young Master,

496
00:33:05,750 --> 00:33:07,070
please understand.

497
00:33:08,480 --> 00:33:09,640
Master

498
00:33:10,110 --> 00:33:12,040
isn't truly heartless toward you.

499
00:33:23,480 --> 00:33:24,880
Today is my birthday,

500
00:33:27,750 --> 00:33:29,750
but my father doesn't want to see me.

501
00:33:33,550 --> 00:33:34,790
Because my birthday

502
00:33:37,350 --> 00:33:39,750
is also the anniversary of mother's death.

503
00:33:43,200 --> 00:33:44,030
Mr. Fei.

504
00:33:46,680 --> 00:33:47,480
Does my father

505
00:33:48,920 --> 00:33:50,440
really hate me?

506
00:33:53,510 --> 00:33:54,310
Young Master,

507
00:33:56,680 --> 00:33:58,640
please don't think that way.

508
00:34:02,310 --> 00:34:03,510
Master just wants you

509
00:34:04,550 --> 00:34:06,270
to not waste any time

510
00:34:07,110 --> 00:34:09,510
and focus on your cultivation,
so you can unleash

511
00:34:09,510 --> 00:34:12,310
the Heaven-and-Earth Strike
as soon as possible.

512
00:34:19,240 --> 00:34:20,000
Mr. Fei.

513
00:34:20,720 --> 00:34:21,160
Yes?

514
00:34:22,710 --> 00:34:24,969
I want to know the story behind this mask.

515
00:34:29,960 --> 00:34:31,510
As for Master's past,

516
00:34:33,000 --> 00:34:33,880
I dare not

517
00:34:34,320 --> 00:34:36,449
presume or make assumptions, either.

518
00:34:40,590 --> 00:34:41,440
I see.

519
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:43,370
[In Memory of Beloved Wife
Dongfang Huaizhu]

520
00:35:40,960 --> 00:35:43,190
With the talents of
the Yiqi Alliance perishing

521
00:35:43,190 --> 00:35:45,190
and chaos rising in the Demon Realm,

522
00:35:45,670 --> 00:35:47,150
I have a way

523
00:35:47,550 --> 00:35:49,110
to turn the current situation around.

524
00:35:49,110 --> 00:35:51,970
As long as
a woman of our Dongfang family is willing,

525
00:35:52,190 --> 00:35:54,920
she can inherit her spiritual power
to her child.

526
00:35:55,360 --> 00:35:57,960
And with the unique secret method
of the Wangquan family,

527
00:35:57,960 --> 00:36:00,690
the child's innate sword spirit
can be awakened,

528
00:36:00,840 --> 00:36:02,300
and the child will possess

529
00:36:02,670 --> 00:36:05,550
the talents of both families.

530
00:36:06,590 --> 00:36:07,400
And that child

531
00:36:08,320 --> 00:36:09,250
will be a Soldier

532
00:36:10,360 --> 00:36:11,560
of the Yiqi Alliance.

533
00:36:12,880 --> 00:36:15,400
What will our child be like?

534
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:16,760
If it's a boy,

535
00:36:18,480 --> 00:36:19,840
he'll be as kind as you.

536
00:36:20,070 --> 00:36:20,920
If it's a girl,

537
00:36:21,360 --> 00:36:22,920
she'll be as smart as you.

538
00:36:23,110 --> 00:36:24,840
What will it take from you then?

539
00:36:25,760 --> 00:36:27,020
Nothing, for the best.

540
00:36:27,320 --> 00:36:28,110
Why?

541
00:36:30,840 --> 00:36:31,590
I think

542
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,880
he'll be like his father,

543
00:36:34,320 --> 00:36:35,850
chasing the endless night,

544
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:37,290
save all living beings,

545
00:36:38,000 --> 00:36:40,000
and becoming an unparalleled hero.

546
00:36:40,280 --> 00:36:41,550
Our child

547
00:36:42,630 --> 00:36:43,960
will definitely become

548
00:36:45,030 --> 00:36:47,160
the strongest swordsman in the world.

549
00:36:48,550 --> 00:36:49,360
Huaizhu.

550
00:36:50,320 --> 00:36:51,760
20 years have passed.

551
00:36:53,480 --> 00:36:56,280
Bamboo Pavilion by River Huai
remains unchanged,

552
00:36:56,760 --> 00:36:57,400
yet I

553
00:36:57,710 --> 00:36:59,320
have grown old.

554
00:37:20,440 --> 00:37:21,370
All these years,

555
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:24,410
in order to make Fugui
the strongest Soldier,

556
00:37:25,000 --> 00:37:25,550
I

557
00:37:27,070 --> 00:37:29,130
haven't been able to be a good father.

558
00:37:31,150 --> 00:37:32,070
And yet, Fugui

559
00:37:34,320 --> 00:37:36,980
has become more and more like
who I was back then.

560
00:37:38,670 --> 00:37:40,600
That is the last thing I want to see.

561
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:52,880
Since he wouldn't meet with Lady Feng,

562
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:55,880
there must be someone
more important he needs to meet.

563
00:38:30,030 --> 00:38:32,490
If you were against
a formidable adversary,

564
00:38:32,710 --> 00:38:34,150
that brief lapse just now

565
00:38:35,150 --> 00:38:36,750
would have been fatal to you.

566
00:38:38,030 --> 00:38:40,160
Today is Mother's death anniversary.

567
00:38:41,030 --> 00:38:42,030
So what?

568
00:38:43,230 --> 00:38:44,590
I want to pay my respects to her.

569
00:38:44,590 --> 00:38:45,650
Pay your respects?

570
00:38:46,670 --> 00:38:47,670
What your mother's spirit in heaven
asks of you

571
00:38:47,670 --> 00:38:51,000
is that you be able to unleash
the Heaven-and-Earth Strike!

572
00:38:51,400 --> 00:38:52,590
Do you know
why you still haven't been able to

573
00:38:52,590 --> 00:38:54,790
unleash the Heaven-and-Earth Strike?

574
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:56,940
Bring it on!

575
00:39:35,230 --> 00:39:36,360
Soft-heartedness!

576
00:39:40,360 --> 00:39:41,160
Attachments!

577
00:39:43,550 --> 00:39:44,480
Unwillingness!

578
00:39:52,280 --> 00:39:53,540
Those are all emotions

579
00:39:53,840 --> 00:39:55,570
that a Soldier shouldn't have.

580
00:39:57,800 --> 00:39:59,150
The weakness deep within your heart

581
00:39:59,150 --> 00:40:02,630
is the reason why you can't unleash
the Heaven-and-Earth Strike!

582
00:40:02,630 --> 00:40:03,480
Father, if I

583
00:40:04,070 --> 00:40:06,000
treat your life like grass or trees

584
00:40:06,360 --> 00:40:08,960
and kill you with my sword
without hesitation,

585
00:40:09,510 --> 00:40:10,840
would you be satisfied?

586
00:40:16,000 --> 00:40:17,110
I want to know why.

587
00:41:07,710 --> 00:41:08,920
Wangquan Hongye.

588
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:10,880
All those tragedies

589
00:41:10,880 --> 00:41:12,880
were caused by you.

590
00:41:13,000 --> 00:41:15,070
You're the one who killed them.

591
00:41:15,840 --> 00:41:17,880
You're the reason

592
00:41:18,110 --> 00:41:20,570
why they all died tragic,
unnatural deaths.

593
00:41:22,400 --> 00:41:24,110
Sometimes, the truth can end up

594
00:41:24,110 --> 00:41:26,040
harming both others and yourself!

595
00:41:31,480 --> 00:41:32,710
Why did you do that?

596
00:41:33,880 --> 00:41:35,340
That Hongye under the mask

597
00:41:35,920 --> 00:41:37,400
is already dead!

598
00:41:38,440 --> 00:41:39,630
He died outside the circle,

599
00:41:39,630 --> 00:41:41,550
under that black Grief Tree!

600
00:41:42,190 --> 00:41:43,800
Your closest friends and loved ones

601
00:41:43,800 --> 00:41:45,660
dying one by one before your eyes—

602
00:41:45,880 --> 00:41:47,810
do you know what that sight is like?

603
00:41:48,960 --> 00:41:51,160
That Hongye underneath the Jinlan Mask

604
00:41:51,230 --> 00:41:52,890
lost because of his emotions.

605
00:41:53,510 --> 00:41:55,360
He'll never forgive himself!

606
00:41:56,630 --> 00:41:59,230
I won't allow you to follow in
his footsteps!

607
00:42:19,590 --> 00:42:20,400
You should go.

608
00:42:22,630 --> 00:42:23,590
Your mother

609
00:42:24,880 --> 00:42:26,070
liked it quiet.

610
00:42:37,170 --> 00:42:41,210
♪ How can the wind stop its course?
How can the clouds stay still? ♪

611
00:42:42,470 --> 00:42:45,320
♪ Joy and sorrow rise and fall,
some sink, some float ♪

612
00:42:47,760 --> 00:42:51,640
♪ Meeting like dew,
like flowers, like mist ♪

613
00:42:52,330 --> 00:42:55,820
♪ You appear vaguely, not far away ♪

614
00:42:57,930 --> 00:43:02,690
♪ My heart undistracted, fully immersed ♪

615
00:43:03,530 --> 00:43:06,550
♪ Loving so deeply,
I forget the way back ♪

616
00:43:05,230 --> 00:43:05,920
Huaizhu.

617
00:43:06,630 --> 00:43:07,710
Over these years,

618
00:43:08,080 --> 00:43:12,990
♪ Cast into desolation,
a lone boat with no one to ferry ♪

619
00:43:08,670 --> 00:43:10,280
Fugui has lost all the joys

620
00:43:10,280 --> 00:43:11,590
a human being should have,

621
00:43:10,630 --> 00:43:14,740
[In Memory of Beloved Wife
Dongfang Huaizhu]

622
00:43:13,480 --> 00:43:15,000
yet I can't go soft on him.

623
00:43:14,000 --> 00:43:16,940
♪ I borrow the bright moon
to express my longing pain ♪

624
00:43:16,110 --> 00:43:16,800
I can't let down

625
00:43:16,800 --> 00:43:19,930
everything you've done for me
and for the Yiqi Alliance.

626
00:43:20,180 --> 00:43:22,860
♪ With countless encounters ♪

627
00:43:20,630 --> 00:43:22,230
The only purpose of a Soldier

628
00:43:22,360 --> 00:43:23,880
is to slay demons.

629
00:43:24,480 --> 00:43:25,440
Grant me

630
00:43:25,290 --> 00:43:30,620
♪ I exchange for your smile in this life,
even if past memories fade away ♪

631
00:43:28,190 --> 00:43:30,000
one last request.

632
00:43:31,020 --> 00:43:35,240
♪ The past cannot be held,
like a dream, like smoke ♪

633
00:43:32,030 --> 00:43:34,090
The Yiqi Alliance's Soldier project

634
00:43:35,230 --> 00:43:36,760
was my plan.

635
00:43:35,880 --> 00:43:39,770
♪ If there's a next life,
we shall meet again ♪

636
00:43:44,040 --> 00:43:47,540
[In Memory of Beloved Wife
Dongfang Huaizhu]

